   {
    "template": "intro",
    "texts": [
     "We don't usually allow filming on buses that are actually in service. However, outside peak commuter hours you can hire a bus that will look like the bus on the route you wish to film, complete with driver."
    ],
    "link": {
     "image": {}
    },
    "image": {},
    "wrapped": false
   },
   {
    "template": "content",
    "texts": [
     "Check your script with the \u003ca href=\"/info-for/media/contact-the-press-office\"\u003ePress Office\u003c/a\u003e before hiring a London bus to film on.",
     "You will also need to get permissions from us before you start to film or photograph on our network. \u003ca href=\"/info-for/media/filming-and-photography/filming-and-photography-on-the-roads\"\u003eContact the red route team.\u003c/a\u003e ",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"Bus stations and depots\"}",
     "You can't film in most working bus stations and depots. Some operators will allow limited filming as long as you meet the costs of providing filming supervision.",
     "If you would like to explore any of these options, please contact one of the bus operators below. In most cases you will need to give at least seven days' notice.",
     "You will also need to provide them with:",
     "{\"template\":\"bulletlist\",\"items\":[\"Proof of insurance\",\"Description of what you will be filming and what the film will be used for\",\"Number of people involved in filming\",\"Times you would like to film\",\"How long you expect to film for\"]}",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"New Routemaster buses\"}",
     "Our iconic New Routemaster buses are available to hire. For more details, please \u003ca href=\"/info-for/media/contact-the-press-office\"\u003econtact our Press Office\u003c/a\u003e .",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"Bus operator contacts\"}",
     "You can usually hire buses from:",
     " \u003ca href=\"http://www.goaheadlondon.com/bus_hire\"\u003eGo-Ahead\u003c/a\u003e ",
     "\u003cstrong\u003eEmail: \u003c/strong\u003e  \u003ca href=\"mailto:commercial.operations@goaheadlondon.com\"\u003ecommercial.operations@goaheadlondon.com\u003c/a\u003e \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePhone\u003c/strong\u003e : 020 8545 6110",
     " \u003ca href=\"http://www.lonutd.co.uk/\"\u003eLondon Utd\u003c/a\u003e ",
     "\u003cstrong\u003eEmail: \u003c/strong\u003e  \u003ca href=\"mailto:hireabus@lonutd.co.uk?Subject=Bus%20hire%20for%20filming\"\u003e hireabus@lonutd.co.uk\u003c/a\u003e \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePhone\u003c/strong\u003e : 020 8400 5502",
     " \u003ca href=\"http://www.metroline.co.uk/vehicle-hire.html\"\u003eMetroline\u003c/a\u003e ",
     "\u003cstrong\u003eEmail: \u003c/strong\u003e  \u003ca href=\"mailto:vehiclehire@metroline.co.uk?Subject=Bus%20hire%20for%20filming\"\u003evehiclehire@metroline.co.uk\u003c/a\u003e \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePhone\u003c/strong\u003e : 020 8218 8879",
     " \u003ca href=\"http://www.ratpdevlondon.co.uk/Privatehire.html\"\u003eQuality Line\u003c/a\u003e ",
     "\u003cstrong\u003eEmail: \u003c/strong\u003e  \u003ca href=\"\"mailto:\"\u003ecomments@qualityline.org\u003c/a\u003e \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePhone\u003c/strong\u003e : 01372 731727 / 731761",
     " \u003ca href=\"http://www.sullivanbuses.com/\"\u003eSullivan Buses\u003c/a\u003e ",
     "\u003cstrong\u003eEmail: \u003c/strong\u003e  \u003ca href=\"mailto:admin@sullivanbuses.com?Subject=Bus%20hire%20for%20filming\"\u003eadmin@sullivanbuses.com\u003c/a\u003e \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePhone\u003c/strong\u003e : 01707 646803"
